          <div class="product__item">
            <h2>BASIC DENIM OVERALL PANT</h2>
            <h2>199144</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="product__item product__item--price">
            <p>Price: 175€</p>
          </div>
          <div class="product__item product__item--size-select">
            <p>SOLD OUT</p>
          </div>
          <div class="product__item product__item--description">
            <p>To re-order sizes XS, S, M, L or XL, contact us using a form <a href="/about">here &rsaquo;.</a></p>
            <p class="mt">
              A basic denim overall pant. At first glance. But if examined closely, when worn, additional styling techniques will emerge; playing with straps,
              using them as a belt, this item can be worn as a regular pant, high waist or low crotch. Deeply hidden, two additional inner pockets will reveal
              themselves only when being carefully looked for.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="product__item product__item--accordion">
            <div class="accordion">
              <div>
                <input type="checkbox" name="panel" id="panel-1" />
                <label for="panel-1">Details</label>
                <div class="accordion__content accordion__content--panel-1">
                  <ul class="accordion__list accordion-panel-1__list">
                    <li>A gender-neutral cut</li>
                    <li>Straps with magnetic buckles</li>
                    <li>6 pocket design: 2 hidden inner pockets, 2 dropped back pockets + 2 side pockets</li>
                    <li>Color: Black</li>
                    <li>Material: 100% raw denim cotton (550 g, 19.4oz)</li>
                    <li>Care: Machine-wash cold, warm (30°C)</li>
                    <li>Proudly created in Croatia from local craftswomen and men</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="product__item product__item--accordion">
            <div class="accordion">
              <div>
                <input type="checkbox" name="panel" id="panel-2" />
                <label for="panel-2">Size & Fit</label>
                <div class="accordion__content accordion__content--panel-2">
                  <ul class="accordion__list accordion-panel-2__list">
                    <li>Karla is wearing size M and is 165cm/5.4 ft tall</li>
                    <li>Boban is wearing M and is 187cm /6.13 ft tall</li>
                    <li>Loose, oversized fit, you can size up or size down</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="product__item product__item--accordion">
            <div class="accordion">
              <div>
                <input type="checkbox" name="panel" id="panel-3" />
